# Trivy ignore list for the Security Audit workflow
# (.github/workflows/security.yml).
#
# One CVE ID or secret rule ID per line, with a comment explaining WHY it
# is ignored and, for unfixed vulnerabilities, a link to the upstream
# issue. Review entries during the monthly security-update window (#392).
#
# Example:
# CVE-2026-12345  # no fix released; mitigated by X; recheck 2026-08
